{
  "id": "adv_main_01_03_02",
  "title": "星見編1章13話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは琴乃ちゃんに\nリーダーをやってほしいんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ I think that {user}-san\nwants you to be the leader.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.72094583665171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "だから私を別のグループに移すって\n言ったんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So the idea to move me out of the group\njust started to make sense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "だとしたらそう言えばいい\n何もわざわざ別グループ作るなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then he should just say so.\nWhy go through the trouble of making another group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.317483091354369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "でも私ね、さっきみんなと話しててね、思ったんだ\n私がいない方が、もしかしたらまとまるのかもって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ when the rest of us were talking‚ I realized something.\nMaybe the group would be better without me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.08414975802105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそんなこと言うの？\nあの人の肩持ちたいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why would you say that?\nAre you taking his side?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.256998399893455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ううん\nそうじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no.\nIt’s not that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ステージを想像するとね、琴乃ちゃんが中心で\nみんなで歌っているのが一番かっこいい気がするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I imagine us on stage‚ and if Kotono-chan is the center‚\nI just feel like that would be the coolest thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.92723520845175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "さっきみんなと話している時\n琴乃ちゃん一杯話してたでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And when we were talking a moment ago‚\nKotono-chan were so passionate about what you were saying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.10343621395254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "これからのこととか\n{user}さんのこととか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way you talked about the future‚\nand about {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.44921906590462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "私、それ聞いてて思ったんだ\n琴乃ちゃん、いざとなればこんなに話せるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listening to you‚ I realized something.\nKotono-chan really can speak your mind when it matters.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの中心になれるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that you have what it takes to be the leader.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.67093306238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……それは……ちょっと頭にきてたから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I just got mad‚ so I blurted it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.71338210756127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はさくらみたいに、みんなを元気にしたり\nうまく会話したりとか出来ないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m not like you‚ Sakura. I don’t have your gift of words.\nYour ability to lift the spirits of those around you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.18611391861778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "それでいいと思うよ\n琴乃ちゃんは琴乃ちゃんのやり方で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that’s fine.\nYou have your own way of doing things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.14610263362071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.64610263362071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "もし私がリーダーだったら\nさくらもアイドル、続けてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I did become the leader‚\nwould Sakura keep being an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.42335889194948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、続けるよ\nこの胸がやりたいって言ってるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ Of course.\nMy heart keeps saying it wants to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.07002564126786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "胸……か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right… Your heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.97238372817176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "うん、最初にここに来た時にも話したでしょ\n私ね、この心臓に命を救われたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. Remember? I told you about it when I first came here.\nThis heart saved my life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7057170615051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "だから、この胸が望んでいることは全部叶えてあげたい\nそうしたいの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I want to give it everything it wishes for.\nThat’s what I want.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.95195634107036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "さくらにはセンターで歌ってほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want you to take center stage‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.41044981108074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.08267202800475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "さくらの歌、凄いと思う\nその歌声をおっきな会場に響かせてほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura's voice is incredible.\nI want to hear it echoing across massive venues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.31600536133809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（やはり琴乃の心には、さくらの歌声が）\n（焼き付いているんだ。姉にそっくりなその歌声が）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So I was right. Sakura’s voice did move Kotono’s heart.）\n（The voice that sounds just like her sister’s.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.86954260295599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "でも…新しいグループって\n言ってたし……まだ、どんな人と一緒になるかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… he said I’d be in a new group.\nAnd I still don’t know who’s gonna be in the group with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.59772494170028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "さくらよりいい歌声の子なんて、いるはずない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guarantee none of them will sing half as good as you‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5643914812104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "私も、さくらみたいに歌えるように頑張る\nだから、さくらは私の目標でいて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to dedicate myself to singing better like you.\nSo please‚ Sakura‚ keep being my role model.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.39772481454384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.16439148121052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.96439148121047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_03_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4310581478771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 155.26439148121057
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
